INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
=========================

For the Impatient
------------------
rails your_survey_app
cd your_survey_app
mv public/index.html public/index.html.old
gem install --no-ri --no-rdoc haml
haml --rails
script/plugin install git://github.com/lazyatom/engines.git
script/plugin install git://github.com/breakpointer/surveyor.git

#
# or: git submodule add git://github.com/breakpointer/surveyor.git vendor/plugins/surveyor
#     git submodule init
#     git submodule update
#

cp vendor/plugins/surveyor/db/migrate/*.rb db/migrate
rake db:migrate

Dependencices
-------------------
Surveyor requires HAML(http://haml.hamptoncatlin.com/download)

Special Considerations for Rails 2.3
-------------------
Rails 2.3 does not yet support plugin migrations. Therefore, you will need to copy Surveyor's migrations to your main application's db/migrate subdirectory.

